  Use
  = link_to 'form builder', root_path
  helper methods to develop form-based applications.

%h2.heading-small.heading-contents Contents:
.grid-row
  .column-two-thirds
    %ul.list.list-contents
      %li
        %a{ href: '#form-text-fields' } Text fields
      %li
